Each source of {{concept filename:"damage" text:"Damage"}} in the game has a damage type, which is used to determine whether the target has any {{concept filename:"resistances" text:"resistance"}} to the damage.

The major damage types are as follows:
  - {{concept filename:"damage_type_kinetic" text:"Kinetic"}}
  - {{concept filename:"damage_type_thermal" text:"Thermal"}}
  - {{concept filename:"damage_type_gas" text:"Gas"}}
